{"data":{"content":{"edges":[{"node":{"id":"d3271b19-9a93-5078-a403-f8111d645ef5","html":"<h2 id=\"前言\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\" aria-label=\"前言 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前言</h2>\n<p>感謝各位這些年來閱讀我的博客文章，以及優化博客系統框架，現在，我將為你帶來一個前後端徹底分離，而且可以一鍵啟動的博客框架。</p>\n<p>如果你希望閱讀英文版本的話，那麼 Github 的 Repo 上面也有提供詳細的文檔。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6Xd4yVQ.png\" alt=\"HomePage\"></p>\n<p>透過這個 Starter，你可以快速建立一個如同 <a href=\"https://calpa.me\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Calpa's Blog</a> 的博客系統。</p>\n<h2 id=\"功能\"><a href=\"#%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\" aria-label=\"功能 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>功能</h2>\n<h3 id=\"系統架構\"><a href=\"#%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%9E%B6%E6%A7%8B\" aria-label=\"系統架構 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>系統架構</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>GatsbyJS v2，更加快速</li>\n<li>Google Analytics</li>\n<li>支持離線操作</li>\n<li>Web App Manifest</li>\n<li>Netlify 網站優化</li>\n<li>精美評論區 (powered by <a href=\"https://github.com/gitalk/gitalk\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Gitalk</a>)</li>\n<li>高速解析 Markdown (基於<a href=\"https://github.com/jonschlinkert/remarkable\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">remarkable</a>)</li>\n<li>支持站點地圖</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"設計\"><a href=\"#%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88\" aria-label=\"設計 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>設計</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>響應式設計</li>\n<li>懶加載（圖片） (基於 <a href=\"https://github.com/ApoorvSaxena/lozad.js\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">lozad.js</a>)</li>\n<li>自動加載 Font Awesome (基於 <a href=\"https://github.com/FortAwesome/react-fontawesome\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">react-fontawesome</a>)</li>\n<li>流暢滑動設計 (基於 <a href=\"https://github.com/cferdinandi/smooth-scroll\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">smooth-scroll</a>)</li>\n<li>分頁設計</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"數據來源\"><a href=\"#%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90\" aria-label=\"數據來源 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>數據來源</h3>\n<ol>\n<li>源自 <a href=\"https://www.contentful.com/\" title=\"Contentful\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Contentful</a>，壹個靈活且易於使用的內容管理系統</li>\n<li>經過系統更新後，你可以使用任意的數據庫</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"可自定的地方\"><a href=\"#%E5%8F%AF%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9\" aria-label=\"可自定的地方 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>可自定的地方</h3>\n<p>如果你覺得這個系統需要更加完善的話，你可以從下面的地方入手：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>搜索引擎優化</li>\n<li>使用 SCSS 來自定義樣式</li>\n<li>數據來源</li>\n</ol>\n<p>如果你喜歡 <a href=\"https://calpa.me\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">我的博客</a>，請給個 star，多謝。以下是如何使用這個博客系統的教程：</p>\n<h2 id=\"前提\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90\" aria-label=\"前提 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前提</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Git</li>\n<li>Node：從 8.5.0 或更高版本開始的任何 8.x 版本</li>\n<li>fork 本項目 （想要貢獻的話）</li>\n<li>在本地計算機上克隆本項目</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"開發\"><a href=\"#%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC\" aria-label=\"開發 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>開發</h2>\n<p>如何運行?</p>\n<ol>\n<li>安裝 Gatsby-CLI</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --global gatsby-cli</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>使用 Gatsby 啟動器創建新的 Gatsby 項目，<code class=\"language-text\">awesome-blog</code>是您博客的文件夾</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\">gatsby new awesome-blog https://github.com/calpa/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>打開文件夾</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-shell line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token function\">cd</span> awesome-blog</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>\n<p>運行開發服務器</p>\n<ol>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">npm start</code> 啟動熱重載開發服務器 (基於<a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Gatsby</a>)</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">open http://localhost:8000</code> 在您喜歡的瀏覽器中打開</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>連接 <a href=\"https://www.contentful.com/\" title=\"Contentful\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Contentful</a> 服務器</p>\n<ol>\n<li>將以下配置添加到<code class=\"language-text\">.env.development</code>文件中</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-text line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-text\">API_SPACE_ID = Your Contentful Space ID\nAPI_TOKEN = Your Content Delivery (Preview) API - access token</code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>如果您使用的是<a href=\"https://www.contentful.com/developers/docs/references/content-preview-api/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Contentful 的預覽 API</a>，那麽所有未發布的內容都將可用。</p>\n<ol>\n<li>您也可以使用其他服務器，只要你提供給 GraphQL 的數據符合系統數據結構。</li>\n</ol>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"配置\"><a href=\"#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\" aria-label=\"配置 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>配置</h2>\n<p>在 <code class=\"language-text\">data/config</code>編輯 exports 的對象</p>\n<p>註意壹下: <a href=\"https://www.colorhexa.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">想要查找 theme_color 十六進制代碼，請單擊此處。</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  title<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your blog title here'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  maxPages<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">12</span>\n  meta<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    description<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'blog description'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    keyword<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'blog, JavaScript'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    theme_color<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'#hexcode'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    favicon<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https:yourimageurl.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    google_site_verification<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your google verification hash'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  name<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your name'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  email<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your_email@gmail.com'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  iconUrl<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://youricon.jpg'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  License<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'by'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  url<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://yourblog.me'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  about<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/2018/05/01/about-your-name/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Sidebar</span>\n  zhihuUsername<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your zhiu user name here'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  githubUsername<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your github user name here'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  friends<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      title<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'friend title'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      href<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'link to their blog'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>插件的配置文件:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">gaOptimizeId<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'GTM-WHP7SC5'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\ngaTrackId<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'UA-84737574-3'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nnavbarList<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    href<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/stats/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    title<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'stat title'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    href<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/tags/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    title<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'tags'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    href<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/guestbook/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    title<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'guestbook'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    href<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/2018/10/04/about-your-blog/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    title<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'your title'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\nredirectors<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    fromPath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    toPath<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'/page/1'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>配置<a href=\"https://gitalk.github.io/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Gitalk</a></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">gitalk<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    clientID<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'18255f031b5e11edd98a'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    clientSecret<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'2ff6331da9e53f9a91bcc991d38d550c85026714'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    repo<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'calpa.github.io'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    owner<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'calpa'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    admin<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token string\">'calpa'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    distractionFreeMode<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"內容模型\"><a href=\"#%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B\" aria-label=\"內容模型 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>內容模型</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>帖子</li>\n</ol>\n<p>要創建帖子，只需提供以下對象模型：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-json line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Post\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"fields\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"title\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Post Title\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"headerImgur\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"header Image Link\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"headerBackgroundColor\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"#66ccff\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"tags\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"tag1, tag2, tag3\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"url\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"awesome-post\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"createdDate\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"new Date() or other dayjs supported datetime value\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"content\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"your markdown content\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"jueJinLikeIconLink\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"掘金 Badge Icon Url\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"jueJinPostLink\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"掘金 Post Url\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li>Headers</li>\n</ol>\n<p>有兩個可配置的 Headers ，分別為 <a href=\"https://calpa.me\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">主頁</a> 和 <a href=\"/tags/\">標簽頁</a>頂部的 #header 。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-json line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"name\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Headers\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"fields\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"purpose\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Tags or Home\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"headerImage\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"header Image\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"createdDate\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"new Date() or other dayjs supported datetime value\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"title\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Display Title\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"titleVisible\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Do you want to show your title in the header?\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"subTitle\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Display a smaller wordings\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"subTitleVisible\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Do you want to show a smaller wordings in the header?\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"部署\"><a href=\"#%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2\" aria-label=\"部署 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>部署</h2>\n<p>我的博客目前正在使用<a href=\"https://www.netlify.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Netlify</a>，當然，您可以使用 Github Pages 作為替代方案。</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Github Pages</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm run deploy</code> 將博客部署到 Github Pages</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Netlify</p>\n<p>自動部署</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"故障排除\"><a href=\"#%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4\" aria-label=\"故障排除 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>故障排除</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>對於 <code class=\"language-text\">window is defined</code>, 引包前檢查 window :</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-javascript line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">typeof</span> window <span class=\"token operator\">!==</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`undefined`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> module <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"module\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm run reset</code> 清除本地緩存</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>查 <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/docs/debugging-html-builds/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">GatsbyJS 調試文檔</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"後記\"><a href=\"#%E5%BE%8C%E8%A8%98\" aria-label=\"後記 permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>後記</h2>\n<p>這個博客系統，是我大學時代一直編寫，然後再進化迭代的一個項目。</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E5%89%8D%E8%A8%80\">前言</a></li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD\">功能</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E7%B3%BB%E7%B5%B1%E6%9E%B6%E6%A7%8B\">系統架構</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88\">設計</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E6%95%B8%E6%93%9A%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90\">數據來源</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E5%8F%AF%E8%87%AA%E5%AE%9A%E7%9A%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9\">可自定的地方</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90\">前提</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC\">開發</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\">配置</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E5%85%A7%E5%AE%B9%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B\">內容模型</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2\">部署</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E6%95%85%E9%9A%9C%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4\">故障排除</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/#%E5%BE%8C%E8%A8%98\">後記</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"前言感謝各位這些年來閱讀我的博客文章，以及優化博客系統框架，現在，我將為你帶來一個前後端徹底分離，而且可以一鍵啟動的博客框架。如果你希望閱讀英文版本的話，那麼 Github 的 Repo 上面也有提供詳細的文檔。透過這個 Starter，你可以快速建立一個如同 Calpa's…","fields":{"slug":"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/"},"frontmatter":{"id":"20181203a","title":"基於 GatsbyJS 的博客系統正式開源：gatsby-starter-calpa-blog，及其使用方法","slug":"/2018/12/03/gatsby-starter-calpa-blog-release-open-source/","date":"2018-12-03T03:48:03.125Z","headerImage":null}},"previous":null,"next":null}]}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"d3271b19-9a93-5078-a403-f8111d645ef5","index":8}}